name: fastbpe
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "fastBPE" %}
{% set version = "0.1.0" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 95eef4be2689e822a918ac4eae3349cd78ca3f28af591afa421f8fac6d4cd889

build:
  number: 4
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv
  skip: True  # [win]

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('cxx') }}
  host:
    - pip
    - python
    - cython
  run:
    - python
    - cython
test:
  imports:
    - fastBPE

about:
  home: https://github.com/glample/fastBPE
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: "C++ implementation of Neural Machine Translation of Rare Words with Subword Units, with Python API."
  doc_url: https://pypi.org/project/fastBPE/
  dev_url: https://github.com/glample/fastBPE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - mxr-conda
    - d-cunningham
    - JennaLipscomb
